name: Dash Rendar (V)
Lore: 'Emperor banished Rendar family from Coruscant. Became gambler and smuggler. Brought down AT-AT at the Battle of Hoth. Works for Rebel Alliance from time to time. Corellian.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting alone (or at same location as opponent''s AT-AT or Imperial), draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and opponent draws no more than one battle destiny here. Dash is a matching pilot for any unique (•) Rogue speeder.',
